data.title: Paisan Original 1957 Polish A1 Movie Poster
data.meta_description: Original 1957 Polish A1 poster by Teresa Byszewska for the first Polish theatrical release of the 1946 film Paisan (Paisa) directed by Roberto Rossellini with Carmela Sazio / Robert Van Loon / Benjamin Emanuel / Raymond Campbell.
